{"article_id":"rZXzit54tRs1am67","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Trump associate Roger Stone has become the latest person in President Donald Trump ' s orbit","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to be sentenced for lying to congress , something","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that has so far not happened to any anti-Trump people","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"who have lied to congress .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Stone was sentenced to 40 months in prison on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"for lying to congress","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and obstructing the FBI ' s investigation","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"into whether the Trump campaign colluded with Russia in 2016","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to steal the election .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Special Counsel Robert Mueller concluded","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"there was no evidence","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that anyone on the Trump campaign colluded with Russia ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"yet Stone was still charged with obstruction .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Judge Amy Berman Jackson ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"who had signaled previously","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that she may give Stone a harsh sentence ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"handed down the sentence on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"\" The court should not just shrug its shoulders","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and say","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"this is a case of ' Roger being Roger , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"according to The New York Daily news .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Jackson , an Obama appointee , went on to say","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that Stone ' s crimes hurt American democracy","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and that letting him off easy would damage the rule of law","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and let partisanship reign supreme .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"\" The truth still exits .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"The truth still matters , \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Jackson said .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"\" For that reason , the dismay and disgust at the defendant ' s belligerence should transcend party . \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"To reiterate ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"no one","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"who was anti-Trump","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and lied to congress","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"has been sentenced .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Former Director of National Intelligence James Clapper , former FBI Director James Comey , and former CIA Director John Brennan have yet to be brought up on lying charges","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"despite evidence","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that they did .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Former FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe just had the investigation into his own lying dropped .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Prosecutors had asked previously","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"that Stone be sentenced up to nine years in prison for his non-violent crimes .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"The prosecutors wrote","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that Stone \" obstructed Congress ' investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 election ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"lied under oath ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"and tampered with a witness. \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Further ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"when he was indicted ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" he displayed contempt for this Court and the rule of law . \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Stone displayed contempt","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"likely because his house was raided early in the morning","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"to make his arrest more dramatic .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"CNN was tipped off to the raid","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"and had cameras set up outside","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"so the nation could watch police forcefully arrest a 67-year-old man","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"who had been charged with non-violent crimes .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The Department of Justice pushed back on the harsh recommendation ,","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"leading to the resignation of all four prosecutors on the case .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"On Thursday Morning , Trump tweeted a segment from Tucker Carlson ' s Fox News program","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"that suggested","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"the president would pardon Stone .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"\" President Trump could end this travesty in an instant with a pardon ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and there are indications tonight","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that he will do that , \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Carlson said in a segment on his show Wednesday night .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Carlson also in that segment called Stone ' s prosecution \" a shocking insult to the American tradition of equal justice . \"","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"Just before 2:00 a.m. , Trump tweeted out the segment ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"but said nothing one way or the other about him pardoning Stone .","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"Other right-leaning commentators have called for Stone to be pardoned ,","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"including Fox News senior judicial analyst Andrew Napolitano .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"Rep. Matt Gaetz","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"( R-FL )","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"has also called for Stone to be pardoned .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":143,"left":128,"right":142,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":110,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":101,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":75,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":1,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":83,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par